---
title: Honey-Soy Pork & Eggplant Salad Bowl with Sesame Avocado & Creamy Dressing
description: Have you ever seen a salad as bright and colourful as this one? Cabbage and pickled carrot make up the base of this bowl, topped off with creamy and crunchy sesame-crusted avocado, tender Asian-spiced pork and crispy golden cubes of eggplant. This dish is already bursting with flavour, but go on, add a drizzle of sesame dressing - you know you want to!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
